[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    189[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mLocation:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m "The Technology" Identity-Patient-And-Workforce-Enrichment subsection (News-and-public-figure-feeds paragraph: "Some health systems integrate news feeds or public-figure databases to elevate scrutiny on patients matching prominent names in current coverage. Useful but requires policy clarity (the system shouldn't be making judgments about who is 'prominent'; it should be implementing policies set by the privacy office)").[K
