[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    642[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The Honest Take's "build the program first" lesson is one of the strongest operational-engineer-voice framings in the recipe. The Implementation-Time Tier table's Basic tier embeds exactly this discipline (4-9 months for the rules-only deployment with manual privacy-office case queue and basic governance). But the two are not explicitly cross-referenced. A reader reading The Honest Take and being convinced of the discipline does not see that the recipe's own implementation-time tiers reflect it; a reader reading the implementation-time tiers does not see The Honest Take's framing of why the Basic tier looks like it does.[K
